title.narrative: Nicaragua Strengthening the Public Health Care System

description.narrative: The Project Development Objectives (PDO) are to: (a) strengthen quality and access to health services; (b) contribute to adapting the public health system to the country’s changing epidemiological profile; and (c) secure financial support in case of Public HealthAlert or Public Health Emergency.
